==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Re-create
<hw>Re`-cre*ate"</hw> <pr>(r?`kr?*?t")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>re-</ets> + <ets>create</ets>.]</ety> <def>To create or
form anew.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>On opening the campaign of 1776, instead of reenforcing, it was
necessary to <qex>re-create</qex>, the army.</q>
<rj><qau>Marshall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Recreate</ent>⟦br⟧
